{
  "text": "Perhaps the utilization of dendrimers could provide an even more elegant nucleation platform as these nanomolecules are even better defined than polymeric nanomatrices. The functional groups of dendrimers have been characterized well [CITATION_1] and could potentially provide a known number of well-defined nucleation sites.",
